<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kjHNsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kjHNsX.png&h=77dee4e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月23日 7pm <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wzpgLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wzpgLQ.png&h=ff902a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每小時留言量<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arsBSiG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarsBSiG.png&h=bf12293c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情幫推這個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKeyS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKeyS</a>"},{"pid":"82b9f48cdb97b32003c222c8f1c7d3bf97a2bdb2","tid":1748053,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"不好太樂觀、畢竟好多區都有素人<br />\n而且我們忽略左中立撚同綠絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae335e276b7441f7b25839f82e295bbd204ecad5","tid":1748053,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日目的只有一個要保皇輸，而運動目的只有一個要真。香港人勝！<br />\n<br />\n不割席！<br />\n不分化！<br />\n不指責！<br />\n不互屌！<br />\n團結一致，方有勝望！<br />\n光服香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"94f1dff2009c47718398285bb0a56ecd77ac6bce","tid":1748053,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，Hong Kong Independence !!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36172e9b19b4fdc3abff11bd6abc902545d16b07","tid":1748053,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=